        <article class="defaultP" margin-top="true">&#xA7; 14-31 bokstav d skal lyde:<ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="d." data-name="d."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1">Lektor med <ul class="defaultList"><li data-li-identifier="1." data-name="1."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-1"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-1-ledd-1">utdanning som omfattar adjunktutdanning godkjend for tilsetjing i grunnskolen</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="2." data-name="2."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-2"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-2-ledd-1">cand.philol.-grad</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="3." data-name="3."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-3"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-3-ledd-1">cand.real.-grad</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="4." data-name="4."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-4"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-4-ledd-1">cand.scient.-grad</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="5." data-name="5."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-5"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-5-ledd-1">cand.polit.-grad</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="6." data-name="6."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-6"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-6-ledd-1">cand.paed.-grad</article></article></li><li data-li-identifier="7." data-name="7."><article class="listArticle" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-7"><article class="legalP" id="kapittel-1-ledd-6-punkt-23-ledd-1-punkt-7-ledd-1">can